com.flowpowered.commons.store.block.impl

Class AtomicShortIntArray

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.flowpowered.commons.store.block.impl.AtomicShortIntArray

  • public class AtomicShortIntArray
extends Object
    An integer array that has a short index. The array is atomic and is backed by a palette based lookup system.

        Parameters:

        variableWidthBlockArray - the array containing the new values, packed into ints
